racker. \n\nWorkout near, go far.", "short_description": "Supernatural offers a complete and connected fitness experience in VR.\n\nSubscribe to Supernatural for fun, rhythm-mapped workouts every day. \n\nDesigned for fitness, Supernatural brings you: \n* Full body, personalized workouts\n* Expert coaching from real trainers\n* Music from top artists\n* Incredible photoreal landscapes\n\nDownload the Supernatural Companion App for your smartphone to start your subscription, connect with friends, and pair an optional heart rate tracker. \n\nWorkout near, go far."}]}, "developer_name": "Within Unlimited, Inc.", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.getsupernatural.com/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.getsupernatural.com/terms", "publisher_name": "Within Unlimited, Inc.", "support_website_url": "https://www.getsupernatural.com/contact", "website_url": "http://getsupernatural.com/", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "810139357995560"}], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED_FOR_SOME_CONTENT", "genres": ["MUSIC", "SPORTS", "EXPLORATION"], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "312048204218745"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 3, "nodes": [{"status": "PENDING", "id": "538004712095967"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "3180939462208430"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "2930768803677213"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "3180939462208430"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1726163700, "status": "PENDING", "id": "538004712